\f3\fs32 \cf5 \strokec5 After Jesus was born in Bethlehem in Judea, during the time of King Herod, Magi from the east came to Jerusalem
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2  
\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 2
\f1\b0 \cf2 \strokec2  
\f3\fs32 \cf5 \strokec5 and asked, \'93Where is the one who has been born king of the Jews? We saw his star when it rose and have come to worship him.\'94
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl432\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\fs32 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 There was a sign - God doesn\'92t ask to have blind faith but grounded faith.\'a0\'a0\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 There is a HUGE difference that I think sometimes people confuse the difference...\cb1 \
