\f1\b0 \cf2 \strokec2  
\f3\fs32 \cf5 \strokec5 When King Herod heard this he was disturbed, and all Jerusalem with him.
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl432\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f3\fs32 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 People get worried when something or someone threatens their authority...we do too.\'a0\'a0It is why we reject Jesus to begin with\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl432\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf2 \cb6 \'a0\
