\f3\fs32 \cf3 \strokec3 (Video clip of Neil Degrasse Tyson explaining why he thinks we live in a simulation - 3 min clip)
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl432\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f3\fs32 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 This is crazy to think through but what I want you to see is one of the smartest and most well known scientists...not philosopher...not priest...scientist, has come to the conclusion that as he looks at the world through the lense of science it makes sense to him that there was a programer.\cb1 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The problem that he has, you have, I have is not in the reality of a programer but the authority of a God.\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl1\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Science points towards a creator who made everything...scientist are more and more coming to this conclusion.\'a0\'a0\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl1\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The issue though is if there is a creator who is God then he has authority over me but if it is just randomness or a kid in his parents basement then who cares.\'a0\'a0\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl1\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Neil says at the end of the clip - \'93I guess it doesn\'92t make any difference\'94.\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl1\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 People will tell me they don\'92t need faith, they have science...they are NOT mutually exclusive.\cb1 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Elon Musk believes in the simulation\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl2\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Francis Collins became a Christian trying to disprove God with Science and discovered the Human Genome\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f4\b \cf7 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 People's problem with God has nothing to do with reality and everything to do with authority!\cb1 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1
\f3\b0 \cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 (Expound here about sin and freedom and we really only have freedom to choose God or choose sin but that is really our only choices)\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl1\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I have seen people run their lives into the ground destroying marriages, finances, relationships...all the while knowing what they are doing is wrong but holding onto the guise of freedom.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 If you are here today and don\'92t believe in God...or maybe somewhat believe but have never come under His authority my question is what will it take?\'a0\'a0What has to happen?\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 (Maybe talk about how Herod died here...may be too strong)\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

