\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 9
\f1\b0 \cf2 \strokec2  
\f3\fs32 \cf5 \strokec5 After they had heard the king, they went on their way, and the star they had seen when it rose went ahead of them until it stopped over the place where the child was.
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\fs32 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I have no clue what this looked like...I don\'92t know if it was a literal star, if others could see it, how bright it was...I don\'92t know.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f4\b \cf7 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 What I do know though is God used a unique way to guide their unique path.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\b0 \cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 He will probably do the same for you.\cb1 \
\ls6\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 This Christmas season you have a unique path and the goal isn't to figure out how God is guiding someone else or what others are doing but what God wants to do in you and through you.\cb1 \
\ls6\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 To follow His calling and path for your life and your life only.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl432\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf2 \cb6 \'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl432\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 10
\f1\b0 \cf2 \strokec2  
\f3\fs32 \cf5 \strokec5 When they saw the star, they were overjoyed.
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2  
\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 11
\f1\b0 \cf2 \strokec2  
\f3\fs32 \cf5 \strokec5 On coming to the house, they saw the child with his mother Mary, and they bowed down and worshiped him.
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f3\fs32 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Why did they want to see this baby?\'a0\'a0WORSHIP!\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What had this baby done?\'a0\'a0NOTHING\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 They worshiped Jesus before they witnessed what He will do\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 It was before.\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We are called to Worship BEFORE we Witness\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 It is so easy to worship after\cb1 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We see this in sports all the time\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl1\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 How many cub fans came out of the wood work AFTER the cubs won the world series?\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Too often we are waiting for God to do a miracle and when He does it then we worship...then we are thankful...then we are ok with it all.\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I really believe the greatest miracles that can happen in our lives come after we worship\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 This Christmas season what if instead of praying, demanding, desiring God to change your situation, worship Him before you witness the miracle.\'a0\'a0\cb1 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl576\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf2 \cb6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 You don\'92t wait for God to show up and then worship but you go first in your worship towards Him in anticipation of what He will do.\cb1 \
